subproject.description: This project supports Parliament in capacity building of Members of Parliament and staff to perform their roles in the multi party political dispensation.
subproject.title: UGA06111 PARLIAMENTARY DEV

subproject.description:
This project aims to support Uganda Human Rights Commission to promote the Rights Based Approach to Development in the Health Sector, Strengthen Capacity of UHRC to handle human rights complaints, to operationalise the Right to Health Desk and popularise the UHRC annual report.

The second activity/output for this project is  funded by OHCHR to support the civil military cooperation centres in North and North Easten Uganda.

A consultancy  on Transitional justice in Uganda will also be casrried out
subproject.title: UGA06112SUPPORT TOHUMAN RIGHTS
